"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sleep with, to make love to","examples":[{"text":"الزوج الوفي يُضاجِع زوجته بحب واحترام.","english":"A faithful husband engages in sexual relations with his wife with love and respect."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to haunt, to bother (e.g. of worry, anxiety)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/dˤaː.d͡ʒa.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25571","headword_ar":"ضَاجِعٌ","root":"DjE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lying upon his side"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any manner;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleeping;"},{"kind":"text","text":"see its verb]; (S, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDoTajiEN","text_ar":"مُضْطَجِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDojiEN","text_ar":"مُضْجِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujaEapN","text_ar":"ضُجَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stupid, foolish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsound in intellect:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K, TA:) because of his impotence, and his cleaving to his place. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalowN DaAjiEapN","text_ar":"دَلْوٌ ضَاجِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A leathern bucket that is full,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, ISk, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it leans in rising from the well by reason of its heaviness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, O, K.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DajuwEN","text_ar":"ضَجُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAjiEN","text_ar":"ضَاجِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  A star"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclining to setting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawaAjiEu","text_ar":"ضَوَاجِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K, TA:) [or]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~awaAjiEu","text_ar":"الضَّوَاجِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [or signifies also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fixed stars."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 364.) ―         -b5-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inclining"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAka DaAjiEFA A_ilaY fulaAnK","text_ar":"اَرَاكَ ضَاجِعًا اـِلَى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I see thee inclining towards such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) ―         -b6-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of bending of a valley:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawaAjiEu","text_ar":"ضَوَاجِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) ―         -b7-  Also, applied to a beast, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Worthless; in which is no good."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [But] ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ganamN DaAjiEapN","text_ar":"غَنَمٌ ضَاجِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Numerous sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaHoEaA='u","text_ar":"ضَحْعَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Fr, S, O, K.) ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibilN","text_ar":"اـِبِلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAjiEapN","text_ar":"ضَاجِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawaAjiEu","text_ar":"ضَوَاجِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Camels keeping to the plants called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remaining among them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","IAar","O","K","ISk"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}